    "content": "Code this constraint in OCL:
For every instance of TextElement, there should exist a TagElement where, in its fragments, there exists at least one TextElement with the same text content as the aforementioned TextElement instance.
        Format the output as a JSON object with the following structure:
        {
            "code": "generated code for the constraint"
        }


        Do not include explanations, examples, or usage demonstrations. Only provide the JSON array.
        "
  },
  {
    "role": "assistant",
    "content": "{"code":"context TextElement inv: \n  TagElement.allInstances()->exists(tag | \n    tag.fragments->exists(fragment | \n      fragment.oclIsTypeOf(TextElement) and \n      fragment.text = self.text))"}"
  }
]

